video.title: Power Rangers Super Samurai
video.synopsis: The Samurai Power Rangers continue their battle against the evil Master Xandred, who has now joined forces with the malevolent Serrator.

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers battle a mutated Nighlok that is using evil Netherworld water to prevent it from drying out as it wreaks havoc throughout the city.
episodes.title: Super Samurai

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers must defeat a Nighlok with an apparently indestructible shell without the help of Antonio, who has unknowingly lost his Samurai Morpher.
episodes.title: Shell Game

episodes.synopsis: When a Nighlok who can trap people's spirits inside common objects disables four Rangers, Mike and Emily determine to defeat him on their own.
episodes.title: Trading Places

episodes.synopsis: Antonio's teammates must help him overcome a disabling fear of fish, while a powerful enemy arrives to help Master Xandred's quest to flood Earth.
episodes.title: Something Fishy

episodes.synopsis: Octoroo, with the help of the Nighlok Eyescar, kidnaps Antonio and Mentor to use as bait in order to lead the rest of the Rangers into a Mooger trap.
episodes.title: The Rescue

episodes.synopsis: A daring boy named Cody unlocks an ancient seal, releasing an enormous BullZord, the very first Samurai Zord, which rampages across the countryside.
episodes.title: The BullZord

episodes.synopsis: Sparks fly when Mia's younger brother comes to town to try to persuade her to sing lead in his band. Meanwhile, Serrator once again attacks the city.
episodes.title: He Ain't Heavy Metal, He's My Brother

episodes.synopsis: When a Nighlok eats his Samuraizer, Kevin is unable to help the team defeat the beast. Meanwhile, Dayu and Deker make a deal with the evil Serrator.
episodes.title: Kevin's Choice

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers battle crafty Nighlok, who creates mirror images of himself, while Spike seeks a job after realizing he must share daily responsibilities.
episodes.title: Runaway Spike

episodes.synopsis: Emily has a crisis in confidence just as the other Rangers are affected by a Nighlok's evil sand, which sends them into a dire hunger/thirst mode.
episodes.title: The Strange Case of the Munchies

episodes.synopsis: After a Nighlok glues their hands together, Kevin and Mike learn that working as a team means knowing when to ask for help with one's weaknesses.
episodes.title: A Sticky Situation

episodes.synopsis: Serrator takes the first step in his evil plan to seize Earth by clouding the minds of the Monalua people, spreading paranoia throughout the island.
episodes.title: Trust Me

episodes.synopsis: As Jayden struggles with doubts about his ability to be the Red Ranger, Master Xandred demands Dayu's Harmonium from Serrator, who reveals his plot.
episodes.title: The Master Returns

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers learn Serrator's new attacks have an ulterior motive: to crack open the earth and let the Sanzu flood it, making him ruler of both worlds.
episodes.title: A Crack in the World

episodes.synopsis: After Serrator asks Deker to complete the last part of his plan, Antonio begs Deker to reconsider his role in the fight between humans and Nighlok.
episodes.title: Stroke of Fate

episodes.synopsis: The Nighlok Fiera unleashes a devastating attack on the Red Ranger, and the Rangers are forever changed when another Red Ranger takes his place.
episodes.title: Fight Fire With Fire

episodes.synopsis: As the Rangers attempt to adjust to being led by a new Red Ranger, Jayden struggles to find new meaning in his life.
episodes.title: The Great Duel

episodes.synopsis: Jayden finishes his grand battle against Deker and the other Rangers try to convince him to rejoin their team before Master Xandred reawakens.
episodes.title: Evil Reborn

episodes.synopsis: With Master Xandred back on Earth, the Rangers attempt to use the Sealing Symbol to stop him, only to discover that he has a new defense against it.
episodes.title: The Sealing Symbol

episodes.synopsis: In a climactic battle, the Rangers face off against Master Xandred for the last time.
episodes.title: Samurai Forever
